    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered and garage-kept its whole life, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. I\u2019ve loved every second with it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this flawless ride. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
